|--------------------------------------------------------------|
|--------------------     PVCS console     --------------------|
|--------------------     v 0.0.5 beta     --------------------|
|--------------------     Installation     --------------------|
|--------------------------------------------------------------|

1. Unzip the PVCS files to a directory on your web server
2. Update $config['base_url'] in application/config/config.php
3. Update user credentials in application/config/pvcs_users.php
4. Done!